com.mozium.api.page.model

Class MoziumWebElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mozium.core.page.MoziumAbstractElement
      • com.mozium.api.page.model.MoziumWebElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMoziumWebAction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MoziumMobileElement

    public class MoziumWebElement
extends MoziumAbstractElement
implements IMoziumWebAction
    This class is the structure that will encapsulate the HTML components of the pages. It expose the DSL of the html elements actions.
    Version:
    1.0.1
    Author:
    mba
